title: Hour 3 - More Baker Reaction, LIV Tour/British Open, David Feherty

Dan provides more insight into the Baker Mayfield trade and other NFL note. And he talks to David Feherty about the upcoming British Open at St. Andrews, Tiger Woods and the LIV Tour.
